metadata.name: Ordinal Project Nyan #1
metadata.description:
Ordinal Project Nyan is a first animated in BTC NFTs chain. 

Each ETH's Ordinal Project Nyan is the only key to get your airdrop ticket to claim the BTC's Ordinal Project Nyan. Your ETH's Ordinal Project Nyan wont burned when you claim your BTC NFT. Claim your BTC's Ordinal Project Nyan by buring the airdrop ticket. You can keep the NFT in both chain.

The Ordinal Project Nyan are inspired by Nyan Cat traits and more exclusive traits created and add to the collection. 

Pay a small fees 2USD++ and 0% royalty to experience the BTC Ordinal Inscription now. And there wont has another public launch after this session.

Private discord for holder and public twitter after sold out and will linked to opensea page. Inscription order will create and start once you burn your airdrop ticket.
